posting_body: ['West Edge', '1430 2nd Ave , Seattle, WA, 98101', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 24', 'OR Text', '24', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'Welcome Home to West Edge', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 527 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'West Edge is perfectly situated in the center of it all, with incredible access to the city’s teeming array of business pursuits, entertainment venues and cultural interests.', 'Your choice of one and two bedroom and Penthouse level homes are part of the awe-inspiring Seattle skyline.', 'West Edge is perfectly balanced on the edge of where you want to be and what you want to do.', 'Pet Policy', 'West Edge is a pet-friendly apartment community.', 'Features include an Indoor and Outdoor Pet Lounge and a Large Dog Run.', 'Please contact our leasing team for details.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', "Key Words: Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation, Paul Allen Brain Science Institute, WeWork, SAM, University of Washington Medicine, NBBJ, Seattle BioMed, Seattle Cancer Care Alliance, Seattle Children's Research Institute, Amazon, Expedia, Facebook, Nordstrom, Swedish Hospital, Nanostring Technologies, Kaiser Permanente, Harborview, Virginia Mason, Microsoft, Google, Boeing, University, Providence Health, University of Washington, Weyerhaueser, Starbucks, Paccar, PEMCO, Safeco, Fletcher Insurance, PATH, Fred Hutchinson, Alaska Airlines, Zillow, Redfin, Downtown, Belltown, Condo, Brand new, luxury, penthouse, concession, free rent, special, Public Transit, Views, Space Needle, SLU, DT, CBD, South Lake Union, Capitol Hill, Water, Pike Place Market, High Rise, Air Conditioning, AC, 24 Hour Concierge, Urban, Modern, Roof Deck, Fitness Center, Yoga, Reserved Parking, Gas Range, Dog Lounge, Views, Fireplaces.", 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'Vzkee1BCGzA']
